properties.areaDesc: Ventura County Mountains; Los Angeles County Mountains excluding the Santa Monica Range
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 10 at 2:40PM PST until January 12 at 3:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Ventura and Los Angeles County Mountains excluding the
Santa Monica Range.

* WHEN...From noon Saturday to 3 AM PST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Strongest winds will be around the
Interstate 5 corridor.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM NOON SATURDAY TO 3 AM PST SUNDAY
